209352511910714708.Text: I came to Thirsk all the way from Cyrodiil, by way of Vvardenfell.  My father once visited Solstheim, you see, and as a boy I was intrigued by his exciting stories of the Nords.  I was particularly fascinated with this very mead hall -- its residents and their adventures, things like that.  I arrived here over a year ago, and have been living among the Nords ever since.  I've been chronicling their lives, and recently collected enough data to complete my history of Thirsk.
